            <td class="pl"><a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/4123514/discussion/22415941/" title="此书观点陈旧，存在硬伤" class="">此书观点陈旧，存在硬伤</a></td>
            <td class="pl"><span class="">来自</span><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mondain/">mondain</a></td>
